OL,3,CDisability campaigners refused entry
OL,4,Cto consultation on benefit reform
OL,6,FITV Granada's Elaine Willcox reports
OL,7,Fon protests in Manchester over
OL,8,Fgovernment plans to reform PIP
OL,9,Fbenefits.
OL,11,FProtests have taken place at a meeting
OL,12,Fin Manchester to discuss government
OL,13,Fproposals on benefits reform.
OL,15,FProtestors gathered at Angel Meadow
OL,16,FPark in the city centre this morning
OL,17,Fat the invite-only consultation on the
OL,18,FDWP Green paper on Pathways to Work.
