OL,3,CDisability campaigners refused entry
OL,4,Cto consultation on benefit reform
OL,6,FThe organisation Disabled People
OL,7,FAgainst Cuts organised the protest at
OL,8,Fthe meeting over fears that benefits
OL,9,Ffor disabled people will be cut back,
OL,10,Fat a time when the cost of living is
OL,11,Fon the rise.
OL,13,FWork and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,14,FKendall announced the cuts earlier
OL,15,Fthis year, mostly from a reduction in
OL,16,Fsupport for those on incapacity or
OL,17,Fdisability benefits. Three million
OL,18,Fpeople are expected to be impacted by
OL,19,Fthe savings.
