OL,3,CDisability campaigners refused entry
OL,4,Cto consultation on benefit reform
OL,6,FMusician Dennis Queen relies on
OL,7,FPersonal Independence Payments and
OL,8,Fsays, "The question is 'Can any of you
OL,9,Fafford to lose a third of your
OL,10,Fincome?' The answer to which is 'no'."
OL,12,F"They don't need to come round the
OL,13,Fcountry, holding meetings, asking
OL,14,Fanyone 'Can you afford to lose a big
OL,15,Fchunk of your income'."
OL,17,FProtestors were unable to get into the
OL,18,Fmeeting and police were called.
