OL,6,FIt's understood that just 20 tickets
OL,7,Fwere issued to the meeting and dozens
OL,8,Fof disabled people were turned away,
OL,9,Fwhich Amnesty International, who
OL,10,Fattended the protest, labelled a
OL,11,Fviolation of people's rights.
OL,13,FAmnesty's Jen Clark says, "Look at
OL,14,Fwhat's happening today, they're asking
OL,15,Fto be let in and have a say, and
OL,16,Fthey're being refused entry."
OL,18,F"You know this isn't OK."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
