OL,6,F"We've written to the Secretary of
OL,7,FState alongside them saying exactly
OL,8,Fthat."
OL,10,FBut the government say they need to
OL,11,Fsave #5 billion, pledging support but
OL,12,Fsaying that the system as it is, can't
OL,13,Fcontinue.
OL,15,F"When it relates to sickness benefit
OL,16,Ffor Universal Credit and PIP, where
OL,17,Falmost one in ten people are receiving
OL,18,Fit, we've got to make sure that it's
OL,19,Fgoing to the people who really need it
OL,20,Fand deserve it more," says Business
OL,21,Fand Trade Secretary Jonathan Reynolds.
